        Load a concept in the browser format. During content authoring previous versions of the concept can be loaded from version control. To do this use the branch path format {branch@yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ss.SSSZ} or {branch@epoch_milliseconds}. The version of the concept when the branch was created can be loaded using {branch@-}.
        Parameters:

        conceptId - conceptId (required)
        acceptLanguage - Accept-Language (required)
